dialogue: *everyone is sitting, staring at the monitor, waiting to see the name the algorithm comes up with*
For once I have no idea..
{8}, I didn't realise you were here.. Do you know who this {20} is?
He was former Officer here at the Agency. One of the best I have ever seen..
He had to be let go due to his out-of-date methods and practices..
Indeed. But I think he is planning something bigger..
Something bigger than firing missiles at us?
Well, with us out of the picture, he would be free to do whatever he liked to London..
My team and I are already looking into the possible whereabouts of our guy. It's going to take some time though, there is a lot of data to sort through..
When is it going to take a short amount of time for once!
*the sound of sirens suddenly fill the room*
Let me guess, the target is the research centre?
Only {endDistance} this time, I guess they couldn't afford to make another big missile!
